# Screenshots Directory

This directory contains screenshots used in the onboarding guide to help users understand the interface and key functionality.

## Screenshot Guidelines

- Use descriptive filenames (e.g., 'main-wallet-interface.png', 'room-creation-form.png')
- Optimize images for web (appropriate file sizes)
- Include proper alt text for accessibility
- Ensure mobile responsiveness for the images
- Take clean, representative screenshots that reduce cognitive load

